She's fighting at
a different location.

26
00:03:06,791 --> 00:03:08,000
Tsubaki!

27
00:03:08,083 --> 00:03:10,958
It's too dangerous
for you out here.

28
00:03:13,958 --> 00:03:15,541
What...?

29
