There are no more Festum left.

32
00:03:30,041 --> 00:03:31,833
All the pilots are
in good condition.

33
00:03:31,916 --> 00:03:33,791
The Fafners are
on their way back.

34
00:03:33,875 --> 00:03:35,416
Commander Makabe.

35
00:03:35,500 --> 00:03:36,916
Yes, what is it?

36
00:03:37,000 --> 00:03:38,375
The pilots have all
been instructed to

37
00:03:38,458 --> 00:03:40,416
head to the medical room.

38
00:03:41,875 --> 00:03:43,000
I understand.

39
00:03:43,083 --> 00:03:45,833
I'll leave you to
take care of them.

40
00:03:46,791 --> 00:03:49,750
Where is Tsubaki
Minashiro right now?

41
00:03:50,791 --> 00:03:52,250
It's strange.

42
00:03:52,333 --> 00:03:54,375
I wonder why they want us all
to meet in the medical room.

43
00:03:55,083 --> 00:03:57,833
Kazuki, do you have any
idea what's going on?

44
00:03:57,916 --> 00:03:59,916
No.
Not a clue.

45
00:04:02,500 --> 00:04:04,250
Soshi...

46
00:04:06,416 --> 00:04:09,208
What happened, Soshi?
Do you know?

47
00:04:10,416 --> 00:04:11,666
Please listen.

48
00:04:11,750 --> 00:04:14,958
Try not to get too upset
when you go inside, Kenji.

49
00:04:16,000 --> 00:04:17,833
Kenji, wait!

50
00:04:28,250 --> 00:04:31,875
No. What happened...
to her?

51
00:04:31,958 --> 00:04:34,666
Why the hell did this happen?

52
00:04:36,500 --> 00:04:39,333
Even the tree is almost dead.

53
00:04:39,416 --> 00:04:40,958
Why's that?

54
00:04:41,333 --> 00:04:42,958
I would like to
know that myself.

55
00:04:43,041 --> 00:04:44,916
Commander Makabe?

56
00:04:45,833 --> 00:04:47,250
Commander Makabe.

57
00:04:47,333 --> 00:04:50,250
This is the first time
that you've come see me.

58
00:04:50,333 --> 00:04:52,083
Tell me something...

59
00:04:52,166 --> 00:04:54,500
Mark Sein's existence,
the abnormalities we're

60
00:04:54,583 --> 00:04:57,541
witnessing in nature, the
enemy's attack patterns...

61
00:04:57,625 --> 00:05:00,541
...and the recent assimilation
of one of our pilots...

62
00:05:00,625 --> 00:05:03,541
All of these things
are related, aren't they?

63
00:05:03,625 --> 00:05:07,458
