becoming parents
away from you,

72
00:05:24,333 --> 00:05:27,541
because it couldn't understand
what it's like to be born.

73
00:05:27,625 --> 00:05:29,833
And so it tried
to protect humans

74
00:05:29,916 --> 00:05:31,791
from death by taking life.

75
00:05:31,875 --> 00:05:35,500
However now... The
MIR is relearning about life.

76
00:05:35,583 --> 00:05:39,250
You mean it's learning about the
concept of life and death?

77
00:05:39,333 --> 00:05:41,083
Is that why it made
all these flowers

78
00:05:41,166 --> 00:05:42,916
on the island blossom suddenly?

79
00:05:43,000 --> 00:05:43,916
Yes.

80
00:05:44,000 --> 00:05:45,416
But there's still
a whole lot more

81
00:05:45,500 --> 00:05:47,583
that it would like
to learn about.

82
00:05:47,666 --> 00:05:49,125
Is that why you've
been coming out here?

83
00:05:49,208 --> 00:05:51,958
So that you can teach
them that during battles?

84
00:05:52,333 --> 00:05:53,750
Have you been
leaking information

85
00:05:53,833 --> 00:05:55,000
about us to the enemy?

86
