Of course she feels sorrow!

91
00:06:07,666 --> 00:06:09,625
Tsubaki wished that she
could've known her father

92
00:06:09,708 --> 00:06:11,583
and mother like a normal child.

93
00:06:11,666 --> 00:06:14,208
