During assimilation
their numbers...

222
00:12:13,250 --> 00:12:15,000
...shape and locale change.

223
00:12:15,083 --> 00:12:16,583
So you see...

224
00:12:16,666 --> 00:12:19,875
That's the reason why the whole
body feels like melted rubber.

225
00:12:19,958 --> 00:12:22,916
Why didn't it happen to Kazuki?
Why's he all right?

226
00:12:23,000 --> 00:12:26,666
I can only speculate that
his mind adapted itself...

227
00:12:26,750 --> 00:12:29,458
There's clearly a higher sense
of self-consciousness from the

228
00:12:29,541 --> 00:12:31,208
bond between Kazuki and Soshi.

229
00:12:31,291 --> 00:12:32,791
