to better themselves

230
00:12:32,875 --> 00:12:34,500
for the sake of the other.

231
00:12:34,583 --> 00:12:38,166
And so perhaps, that is the
biggest factor influencing it.

232
00:12:38,250 --> 00:12:40,166
It's impressive,
but Kazuki couldn't have

233
00:12:40,250 --> 00:12:41,833
progressed to that
level on his own...

234
00:12:41,916 --> 00:12:43,416
Right?

235
00:12:43,500 --> 00:12:46,000
Which means we have no idea how
well the Mark Sein will do in

236
00:12:46,083 --> 00:12:48,250
remote operations when
it no longer has direct

237
00:12:48,333 --> 00:12:51,166
communication with the
Siegfried System.

