00:13:33,666 --> 00:13:36,708
So he asked for your
advice as well Dr. Tohmi?

259
00:13:36,791 --> 00:13:38,125
Yes.

260
00:13:38,208 --> 00:13:40,416
He wanted to know
approximately how much time

261
00:13:40,500 --> 00:13:43,750
he would have before he would
completely lose consciousness.

262
00:13:45,833 --> 00:13:46,791
It seems...

263
00:13:46,875 --> 00:13:49,250
...that I don't have
much time left.

264
00:13:49,833 --> 00:13:51,916
What are you
going to do, Soshi?

265
00:13:52,000 --> 00:13:55,583
I have prepared myself for
the worst possible outcome.

266
00:13:55,666 --> 00:13:57,333
I see...

267
00:13:57,416 --> 00:13:58,625
We weren't able to
become actual

268
00:13:58,708 --> 00:14:01,916
brother and sister
until the end, huh?

269
00:14:02,000 --> 00:14:04,250
I saw you for the
first time ten years ago.

270
00:14:04,333 --> 00:14:06,916
My father took me to see you.

271
00:14:07,000 --> 00:14:08,291
I remember.

272
00:14:08,375 --> 00:14:11,416
Ever since then, I have
visited you many times.

273
00:14:11,500 --> 00:14:13,000
I know.

274
00:14:13,583 --> 00:14:16,333
I lived to protect
you and the island.

275
00:14:16,416 --> 00:14:17,791
At least...

276
00:14:17,875 --> 00:14:19,250
...that's what I thought.

277
00:14:19,333 --> 00:14:23,166
You thought that until you
were hurt by Kazuki, right?

278
00:14:23,250 --> 00:14:26,375
Tell me what you
want to do Soshi.

279
00:14:26,458 --> 00:14:27,791
If in the end, we join the

280
00:14:27,875 --> 00:14:30,416
Neo U.N.'s
final battle operations...

281
00:14:30,500 --> 00:14:33,291
...I want to fight
alongside all of my friends.

282
00:14:33,375 --> 00:14:35,166
Therefore I'd like
to leave this island.

283
00:14:35,250 --> 00:14:37,416
And so I need the
core's permission.

284
00:14:37,500 --> 00:14:41,041
Don't you realize that you
already left me long time ago.

285
00:14:41,125 --> 00:14:42,625
However...

286
00:14:42,708 --> 00:14:46,458
...you won't be able to be with
them for a long period of time.

287
00:14:46,541 --> 00:14:49,000
Even with the extra stress of
the Siegfried System

288
00:14:49,083 --> 00:14:50,291
and Fafner placed on me,

289
00:14:50,375 --> 00:14:52,875
I can still operate
for about eighteen hours.

290
00:14:52,958 --> 00:14:56,083
And in that time, if you
are with the most important

291
00:14:56,166 --> 00:14:58,625
people to you, you are
the happiest, correct?

292
00:14:58,708 --> 00:15:00,125
That's right.

293
00:15:00,208 --> 00:15:02,041
In that case,
don't worry about me.

294
00:15:02,125 --> 00:15:03,416
Go right ahead.

295
00:15:03,500 --> 00:15:05,875
I hope I'll still be able
come outside and watch,

296
00:15:05,958 --> 00:15:08,166
so I can see you off.

297
00:15:08,916 --> 00:15:10,833
I'm so sorry...

298
00:15:10,916 --> 00:15:14,666
I appreciate this.
Thank you.

299
00:15:14,750 --> 00:15:17,458
Now you have
no choice but to fight.

300
00:15:17,541 --> 00:15:18,833
I hope someday you'll remember

301
00:15:18,916 --> 00:15:21,000
that there's also
a different way.

302
00:15:21,083 --> 00:15:22,333
I will.

303
00:15:22,416 --> 00:15:25,750
Oh! And another thing,
don't forget me okay?

304
00:15:27,666 --> 00:15:29,083
I won't.

305
00:15:30,083 --> 00:15:31,958
I promise.

306
00:15:36,083 --> 00:15:37,583
Canon Memphis?

307
00:15:37,666 --> 00:15:38,916
Yes.

308
00:15:39,000 --> 00:15:41,083
She demands to be injected
with alien biomaterial.

309
00:15:41,166 --> 00:15:43,000
She's locked herself
in the medical room.

310
00:15:43,083 --> 00:15:46,083
And she refuses to battle
if her demands are met.

311
00:15:46,166 --> 00:15:47,375
She probably thought someone

312
00:15:47,458 --> 00:15:49,458
was giving an order
when they weren't...

313
00:15:49,541 --> 00:15:50,750
Then again...

314
00:15:53,416 --> 00:15:54,750
Without knowing
your reasons for it...

315
00:15:54,833 --> 00:15:56,833
...I cannot give
you this injection!

316
00:15:56,916 --> 00:15:58,708
Please. Canon.

317
00:15:58,791 --> 00:16:00,916
Just tell us who
told you to do this?

318
00:16:01,000 --> 00:16:01,916
Uh...

319
00:16:02,000 --> 00:16:03,375
Look.

320
00:16:03,458 --> 00:16:06,041
Once you tell us the truth,
We'll inject this in you.

321
00:16:06,125 --> 00:16:07,666
So just tell us.

322
00:16:07,750 --> 00:16:10,166
No, stop it!
You can't!

323
00:16:10,250 --> 00:16:11,708
Kazuki was the one.

324
00:16:11,791 --> 00:16:12,458
What?

325
00:16:12,541 --> 00:16:14,208
He did?
When was this?

326
00:16:14,291 --> 00:16:17,500
It was back when I tried to
disappear along with the island.

327
00:16:17,583 --> 00:16:20,208
Kazuki told me I had
to make my own choice.

328
00:16:20,291 --> 00:16:21,583
But this is?

329
00:16:21,666 --> 00:16:22,708
Not just him...

330
00:16:22,791 --> 00:16:24,208
Mrs. Hazama said it too...

331
00:16:24,291 --> 00:16:26,000
She said that I
had to live without orders.

332
00:16:26,083 --> 00:16:27,166
Wait just a minute.

333
00:16:27,250 --> 00:16:29,750
That isn't what
I was getting at, at all!

334
00:16:30,583 --> 00:16:32,541
I've had hard times.

335
00:16:32,625 --> 00:16:34,750
And I've thought...
quite a lot.

336
00:16:34,833 --> 00:16:38,541
In the end...
there's only one solution.

337
00:16:40,000 --> 00:16:43,083
I'm making a
choice once and for all.

338
00:16:43,166 --> 00:16:47,791
And this here is my choice.
To be on this island.

339
00:16:50,833 --> 00:16:53,458
I'm going now.

340
00:16:58,166 --> 00:17:00,250
I'm going too...

341
00:17:00,333 --> 00:17:02,625
...Sakura.

342
00:17:04,000 --> 00:17:06,416
Enemy sighted
120 kilometers away.

343
00:17:06,500 --> 00:17:08,541
It's on approach.
There appears to only be one.

344
00:17:08,625 --> 00:17:10,791
We've identified it
as a Scarabee-type.

345
00:17:10,875 --> 00:17:12,375
However it could be
a new mutation.

346
00:17:12,458 --> 00:17:13,625
There's only one of them?

347
00:17:13,708 --> 00:17:15,458
I guess as soon
as Sakura collapsed,

348
00:17:15,541 --> 00:17:17,333
they changed their patterns.

349
00:17:17,416 --> 00:17:19,541
I have no doubt that the
previous two hundred enemies

350
00:17:19,625 --> 00:17:22,458
deployed were sacrificed in
order to exhaust our pilots and

351
00:17:22,541 --> 00:17:24,750
increase their
odds of assimilation.

352
00:17:24,833 --> 00:17:26,375
Attack the enemy
with full force!

353
00:17:26,458 --> 00:17:27,875
Let's show them
just how ineffective

354
00:17:27,958 --> 00:17:29,250
their war of attrition is.

355
00:17:29,333 --> 00:17:30,375
Sorry I'm late.

356
00:17:30,458 --> 00:17:31,458
You okay?

357
00:17:31,541 --> 00:17:32,541
I'm all right now.

358
00:17:32,625 --> 00:17:34,500
Ok, number one
and two Welle Shields

359
00:17:34,583 --> 00:17:36,750
are ready to be deployed.

360
00:17:37,375 --> 00:17:38,875
I've never fought
in a Fafner for real.

361
00:17:38,958 --> 00:17:41,041
I've only done
it in the simulators.

362
00:17:41,125 --> 00:17:42,916
Yeah. I've
never done it either.

363
00:17:43,000 --> 00:17:45,291
There's no need to worry.

364
00:17:45,375 --> 00:17:46,791
What are you doing here?

365
00:17:46,875 --> 00:17:49,041
I'm gonna defeat
all the enemies.

366
00:17:50,541 --> 00:17:51,500
That's right.

367
00:17:51,583 --> 00:17:54,291
Here.
It's for you.

368
00:17:54,791 --> 00:17:55,791
It's for luck.

369
00:17:55,875 --> 00:17:58,375
Wear it and it
will keep you safe.

370
00:18:06,833 --> 00:18:09,666
Mark Sieben, check out the
enemy's defensive capabilities

371
00:18:09,750 --> 00:18:11,791
and determine if
this is a new type.

372
00:18:11,875 --> 00:18:13,791
Mark Acht, Funf, and Babalon,

373
00:18:13,875 --> 00:18:17,083
you three will come in direct
contact with the enemy.

374
00:18:18,458 --> 00:18:21,166
Megaselion and Mark Sein
will analyze the enemy's

375
00:18:21,250 --> 00:18:24,083
method of attack and try to
capture it from behind.

376
00:18:24,166 --> 00:18:27,041
Whatever happens,
don't break this formation.

377
00:18:27,125 --> 00:18:29,458
The Denial Defense Line
is about to be crossed.

378
00:18:29,541 --> 00:18:31,750
All right Mark Sieben,
begin your attack!

379
00:18:31,833 --> 00:18:33,166
Roger.

380
00:18:41,958 --> 00:18:43,250
Huh?

381
00:18:45,750 --> 00:18:47,916
Eject the cockpit bloc!

382
00:18:48,416 --> 00:18:50,500
Did you see that?
What the hell happened?

383
00:18:50,583 --> 00:18:52,750
Mark Funf, retreat.

384
00:18:52,833 --> 00:18:54,541
Babalon and Mark Acht,
keep your distance

385
00:18:54,625 --> 00:18:56,958
and intercept it
from both sides!

386
00:19:09,875 --> 00:19:11,750
How did it...?

387
00:19:13,291 --> 00:19:15,541
Why isn't the pain
inhibitor working?

388
00:19:15,625 --> 00:19:17,041
This makes no
sense the data isn't

389
00:19:17,125 --> 00:19:18,875
showing any damage anywhere...

390
00:19:18,958 --> 00:19:19,750
Canon!

391
00:19:19,833 --> 00:19:20,958
Got it!

392
00:19:24,750 --> 00:19:26,958
There.
We're back online.

393
00:19:30,541 --> 00:19:32,291
Why...?

394
00:19:32,708 --> 00:19:35,291
...why isn't it attacking us?

395
00:19:35,375 --> 00:19:39,416
The enemy is merely sending all
of our attacks back towards us.

396
00:19:39,500 --> 00:19:41,666
It isn't attacking
or assimilating us?

397
00:19:41,750 --> 00:19:43,166
That means...!

398
00:19:43,250 --> 00:19:44,583
Yes.
That's right.

399
00:19:44,666 --> 00:19:47,208
It has understood your pain.

400
00:19:49,916 --> 00:19:51,833
Mark Funf, launch
the Aegis equipment

401
00:19:51,916 --> 00:19:53,333
and try to hold off the enemy.

402
00:19:53,416 --> 00:19:54,458
Roger!

403
00:19:56,125 --> 00:19:59,250
Here I go!

404
00:20:01,750 --> 00:20:03,750
Mark Sein, approach
the enemy from behind

405
00:20:03,833 --> 00:20:05,041
and try to immobilize it.

406
00:20:05,125 --> 00:20:06,208
Understood.

407
00:20:12,791 --> 00:20:15,333
Good.
Now keep on crushing it.

408
00:20:25,208 --> 00:20:26,416
Kazuki!

409
00:20:32,208 --> 00:20:34,833
Assimilation...
Oh no.

410
00:20:40,041 --> 00:20:42,541
The enemy is beginning
to spread its roots.

411
00:20:46,500 --> 00:20:47,916
Soshi...

412
00:20:48,000 --> 00:20:49,750
The enemy has now
reached the Keel Block!

413
00:20:49,833 --> 00:20:51,166
What?!

414
00:20:58,250 --> 00:21:01,833
Was it trying to take over
the system from the start?

415
00:21:02,666 --> 00:21:05,041
Assimilation with the
Siegfried System has started.

416
00:21:05,125 --> 00:21:07,333
Separate the enemy's
main body from its roots!

417
00:21:07,416 --> 00:21:09,208
You bastard!

418
00:21:25,625 --> 00:21:27,208
Soshi...

419
00:21:27,291 --> 00:21:30,291
Ask Kazuki...
if he can lend me a hand...

420
00:21:30,375 --> 00:21:31,750
Kazuki!

421
00:21:31,833 --> 00:21:34,333
I need you to try
and move your hand?

422
00:21:38,916 --> 00:21:40,000
Good enough!

423
00:21:40,083 --> 00:21:42,833
I won't let them feel
sad any longer...

424
00:21:42,916 --> 00:21:46,125
I'll protect you!

425
00:21:53,958 --> 00:21:55,500
Eject now!

426
00:22:33,833 --> 00:22:38,791
♪ closing song ♪

427
00:23:38,916 --> 00:23:41,500
Power that's been taken.

428
00:23:42,541 --> 00:23:45,000
Hope that's been taken.

429
00:23:46,291 --> 00:23:48,875
Yumi... ko...

430
00:23:50,458 --> 00:23:54,791
Next on Fafner episode
number twenty-three.

431
00:23:56,541 --> 00:23:58,333
"Decoy."

432
00:23:59,458 --> 00:24:01,583
Are you there?

